flowchart TD
    A[Power On / Reset] --> B[Boot ROM]
    B --> C[SPL / MLO]
    C --> D[U-Boot]
    D --> E[Kernel Entry]
    E --> F[Kernel Initialization]
    F --> G[OS Running]

    B:::vendor
    C:::boot
    D:::boot
    E:::kernel
    F:::kernel

    classDef vendor fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;
    classDef boot fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;
    classDef kernel fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;